verbose_text: MUC5B also induce mucin secretion in chronic bronchitis and cystic fibrosis by a variety of inflammatory mediators such as bacterial lipopolysaccharide (LPS), interleukin-1beta, tumor necrosis factor-alpha and leukotriene D 4.
